verbose_text: If NEFDI < 0, then NEFDI = 0, where the in situ damage index, ISD i, is expressed as (12) ISDi = sumomega = ab {(| Hdi (omega) |-| Hui (omega) |) 2x (Dmax)-1} n, where a, b, and n are working parameters and D max is given by (13) Dmax = max [{| Hdi (omega) |} max, {| Hui (omega) |} max].
